data.description: This Tudor is Practically Perfect in Every Way! Fall in love from the moment you turn on to 45th St, and pull up to this stunning home! Walk into the front door to gleaming newly refinished hardwood floors, new paint throughout, new carpet, tons of amazing natural light, newer double pane windows, large living room, fabulous dining room, beautiful kitchen with quartz counter tops, tons of storage, a cozy extra room for an office, media room, or first floor play room, walk upstairs to oversized bedrooms, tons of storage, amazing bathrooms, and so many more updates! Next walk outside to the backyard that has an amazing back deck that is perfect for entertaining, evening dinners, wine and great conversations with family and friends, and additional storage building behind the 2 car garage! You won’t want to miss this opportunity to own your slice of heaven i Mayfair Heights! You will love the neighbors, the neighborhood, the location is amazing, and so much more! This house has been loved by the same family for nearly 2 decades with tons of love and amazing memories, it’s ready for its next family to make it their amazing home with fabulous memories! Call today for your private showing!
